      • initBuilder

        public T initBuilder(java.lang.String componentKeyName,
            AFSwinxConnection modelConnection,
            AFSwinxConnection dataConnection,
            AFSwinxConnection sendConnection)
        This method init builder. It set existed connection to builder. There are connection types, which are used to retrieve model definitions, data and post data back.
        Specified by:
        initBuilder in interface ComponentBuilder<T>
        Parameters:
        componentKeyName - key in which you should retrieve this component back and do other staff with it
        modelConnection - connection to end point where model is defined couldn't be null
        dataConnection - connection to end point where data are, if null then component will be empty
        sendConnection - connection to end point where will be send update or insert request if null no request is send. It also could be used HTTP method as put, send and delete.
        Returns:
        it returns this builder which could be used to build AFSwinxTopLevelComponent
